  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Your invoice starts on the 1st of the month <span class="font-semibold">after</span> your free trial ends, no matter when you sign. If your trial ends on <span class="font-semibold">March 17</span>, I'll eat the cost for the rest of March, invoice you for <span class="font-semibold">April 1</span> – <span class="font-semibold">March 31</span>, and make sure you never lose access. I'm also happy to charge for partial terms to align with budget cycles.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Invoices are emailed (via Stripe) with <span class="font-semibold">full remittance details</span>. Pay by <span class="font-semibold">card</span>, <span class="font-semibold">ACH</span>, or <span class="font-semibold">wire</span>. Net 30 only.
